{"tid":1019894,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次紋身 關於我同女友","createTime":"2019-02-13T08:56:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T12:05:24.000Z","uid":29974,"like":1,"dislike":61,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"ec6b84a837d7027b9d656e621fcf1f8e417add4c","tid":1019894,"uid":29974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"同女友異地戀四年 感情一直都好好 <br />\n一個係香港 一個係杭洲 <br />\n大家都各自打拼緊 燕子代表我地 希望有朝一日 <br />\n可以一齊打造我地既愛巢 <br />\n原來紋身會上癮 紋完會覺得好似仲唔夠咁 <br />\n之後應該會再補其他落去 希望係我同佢既仔女<br />\n個紋身佢仲未知 打算情人節佢飛過黎個陣比個驚喜佢 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FeDD6Wu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFeDD6Wu.png&h=401ece1a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"425747a649c2e830330be6fe421fbdcb8ca2fe79","tid":1019894,"uid":50658,"like":78,"dislike":0,"score":78,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:57:53.000Z","msg":"分飛燕<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">真心祝福你</span></span>"},{"pid":"90750bbd92fec9f794f20247d59a7cff163b49e9","tid":1019894,"uid":3480,"like":24,"dislike":0,"score":24,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:58:12.000Z","msg":"傻閪先紋條女係身<br />\n仲要紋大陸閪"},{"pid":"3f3bc498082b4a5385eac95cd1b0c15610f2471f","tid":1019894,"uid":187076,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:59:03.000Z","msg":"分開左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cfb5552a353922a595680c82a15075e244822e6","tid":1019894,"uid":229789,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:59:04.000Z","msg":"唔該你到時結婚上返去同佢住，唔好返嚟香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa41d7d41ca6f09a0af2f9295c071a8ae9ba18ca","tid":1019894,"uid":184768,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-13T08:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecc9d3614b7a4bd41cc333930a5140